@Node "What is this ?"

                     @{fg fill}What is this ?@{fg shadow}

 This is a serial mouse driver.
 You can use all Microsoft compatible 2 buttons serial mouses
 and SolePointer with 4800 baud rate.
  
 Default baud setting is 1200 like a Microsoft serial mouse.
 If you do not want to change it, do not press any button.

 If you want to change the baud rate to 2400, press and hold
 the left button. 

 If you want to change the baud rate to 4800, press and hold
 the right button. 

 Enter SoleMouse to execute from CLI.
 From Startup-Sequence use this line:

 Run <>nil: SoleMouse

 The indicator on the mouse will flash once,
 to indicate that device is installed for 1200 bauds,
 twice for 2400 bauds, and three times for 4800 bauds.
 Release your hold on the button. The baud rate you choise
 is now installed.

 Note: Driver doesnt use the serial preferences.

 Email: prohst03@vm.ege.edu.tr (OR)
@endnode
